name: Dyson Sphere
description: A structure that completely surrounds a star to capture its energy.

name: Stellar Engine
description: A megastructure for moving or controlling stars.

name: Matrioshka Brain
description: A computer the size of a solar system.

name: Computronium
description: Matter organized for maximum computational efficiency.

name: Self-Replicating Machine
description: A machine that can create copies of itself.

name: Nanobot
description: A microscopic robot capable of manipulation at the atomic level.

name: Nanite Swarm
description: A collection of nanobots working together.

name: Molecular Assembler
description: A device that builds objects atom by atom.

name: Matter Replicator
description: A device that creates matter from energy.

name: Energy-to-Matter Converter
description: A device that transforms energy into physical matter.

name: Consciousness Upload
description: Transferring a mind into a digital form.

name: Digital Immortality
description: Existing as a digital entity indefinitely.

name: Artificial General Intelligence
description: An AI with human-level cognitive abilities.

name: Superintelligence
description: An AI that far exceeds human intelligence.

name: Singularity
description: The point where AI surpasses human intelligence.

name: Self-Evolving AI
description: An AI that can improve itself autonomously.

name: Quantum AI
description: An AI that uses quantum computing.

name: Neural Lace
description: A mesh that integrates with the brain.

name: Full Dive VR
description: Virtual reality that feels completely real.

name: Simulated Reality
description: A reality created by advanced computation.

name: Parallel Universe Access
description: Accessing alternate realities or dimensions.

name: Dimensional Portal
description: A gateway to other dimensions.

name: Reality Manipulation
description: The ability to alter physical laws.

name: Time Manipulation
description: The ability to control the flow of time.

name: Chronos Engine
description: A device for time travel or time manipulation.

name: Causality Violation
description: Acting in ways that break cause and effect.

name: Grand Unified Theory
description: A theory that unifies all physical forces.

name: Theory of Everything
description: A complete description of physical reality.

name: Universal Constructor
description: A device that can build anything.

name: Omega Point
description: The hypothetical final state of the universe.

name: Post-Scarcity Economy
description: An economy where resources are unlimited.

name: Resource Synthesis
description: Creating any resource from basic materials.

name: Infinite Energy Source
description: A source of unlimited energy.

name: Zero-Point Energy
description: Energy extracted from the quantum vacuum.

name: Vacuum Energy Harvester
description: A device that extracts energy from empty space.

name: Black Hole Engine
description: A device that extracts energy from black holes.

name: White Hole Generator
description: A device that creates white holes.

name: Exotic Matter
description: Matter with unusual properties not found in nature.

name: Negative Mass
description: Matter with negative mass. Enables exotic physics.

name: FTL Communication
description: Communication faster than the speed of light.

name: Tachyons
description: Hypothetical particles that travel faster than light.

name: Universal Translator
description: A device that translates any form of communication.

name: Omniscience Device
description: A device that knows everything.

name: Reality Engine
description: A device that can create or modify reality.

name: God Machine
description: A machine with god-like capabilities.

name: Transcendence
description: The state of existing beyond physical limitations.

name: Post-Physical Existence
description: Existing without a physical body.

name: Universal Consciousness
description: A consciousness that encompasses everything.

name: Infinite Being
description: An entity without limits.

name: Ascension
description: The ultimate evolution beyond all known forms.
